-- MOVES-Pictet Asset Management hires 3 executives from Baring Asset Management
-- 
-- Tue Sep 02, 2014 10:46AM EDT
-- None



Sept 2 (Reuters) - Pictet Asset Management Ltd said it hired three portfolio managers from Baring Asset Management to strengthen its international multi asset capability.

Percival Stanion, Andrew Cole and Shaniel Ramjee will join Pictet in the coming months and will be based in London, Pictet said. Stanion will join as head of multi asset strategies, excluding Switzerland. He will be named the company's vice chairman, Pictet said.